title = "The Mysterious Man";
content = oHero.name+" and his band encountered a cloaked figure, dressed head to toe in heavy black rags that shifted and slithered as if alive itself. " + oHero.name +" felt uneasy upon the sight of the man, questioning the man as to why he had approached his band. The man's whispers were painful and breath foul as he preached: \n\n 'The Dead do not wait for those who bare the rags.' \n \n He stretched an arm and his weighted rags extended toward "+oHero.name+", almost in offering."
